        "id": 1381059
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-11-24T18:46:19Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I remember the reason I didn\u0027t use pointer is that none of the function is supposed to modify any value inside the mask. Do you think we should use pointer instead?",
      "parentUuid": "eb2e9e49_25e88031",
      "revId": "8c7b8843fb7b389719f9d1a7bf093e88791999f4",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba"
    },
    {
      "unresolved": false,
      "key": {
        "uuid": "4fe9196a_3017e064",
        "filename": "/PATCHSET_LEVEL",
        "patchSetId": 6
      },
      "lineNbr": 0,
