      "writtenOn": "2020-11-24T20:30:23Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Read https://github.com/golang/go/wiki/CodeReviewComments#receiver-type and I think it make sense to use pointer as the size of Mask will grow proportionally to the # and depth of input fields. I\u0027ll make the change today (maybe tomorrow).",
